Package io.github.ai4ci.output

Interface PersonDemographicsCSV

All Superinterfaces:
CommonCSV.Execution, CommonCSV.Model, OutputWriter.Writeable
@Immutable public interface PersonDemographicsCSV extends CommonCSV.Execution
Person demographic records exported at simulation start.

Main purpose: provide per‑agent demographic and baseline attributes such as age, mobility baseline and location. Records are produced at the START stage and are written per agent to a DuckDB database (demog.duckdb).

Downstream uses: used for descriptive statistics, stratified analyses and as a join table for other per‑agent outputs such as line lists.

Author:
Rob Challen
